node.text:
“Meet your fear, until your fear becomes your FUN ! @iamjoelbrown ✨
There were so many amazing experiences in the last year of traveling, all because I said YES to life. I said YES to traveling solo.  And I said YES to doing something beyond my comfort zone.
✨
Sure, it was a bit scary, but now it’s fun! Thanks brother Joel for the inspo.
✨
I’ve learned that putting yourself into new situations can drive depressive thoughts out by replacing them with new discoveries and super cool experiences . You see, we don’t remember those times where we played it small, but in the end, we’ll be able to see how well we lived our life.
✨
Tell me a new experience that forced you out of your comfort zone, and let’s encourage our peeps! 💫
📸: @simplyfreshsanmarino 
#mentalhealthawarenessmonth #depressionhelp #lynncanyonsuspensionbridge#VeryVancouver
#CurrentlyGraced
@mariakarras I’ll be back next week. Call me. Same number😊
You are so inspiring. I’m solo now too and want to hear your story of traveling solo. When are you back?
WOW, such a great profile, thanks for sharing! You would be perfect for our team, DM me so we can network more ;)!!
